  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single-center, retrospective, open-label study. This study is planned to
      investigate the accuracy of mRS and NIHSS, comparing with the accuracy of CSF pressure and
      papilledema grade in assessing cerebral venous sinus thrombosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
